headline: Healthpeak Properties Reports Fourth Quarter and Year Ended 2024 Results and Increases Cash Dividend
summary: DENVER, February 03, 2025--Healthpeak Properties, Inc. (NYSE: DOC), a leading owner, operator, and developer of real estate for healthcare discovery and delivery, today announced results for the fourth quarter and year ended December 31, 2024.
